        <span class="feature-icon">üìÑ</span>
        <h4>5 Deep-Dive Casefiles</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">Each investigation is 3,500+ words of forensic analysis</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature card">
        <span class="feature-icon">üìä</span>
        <h4>Evidence Maps</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">Visual breakdown of every source with A-D grades</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature card">
        <span class="feature-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</span>
